import React from 'react'
import Button from 'react-bootstrap/esm/Button'
import Container from 'react-bootstrap/esm/Container'
import TypeModal from '../components/modals/TypeModal'

const AdminPanel = () => {
  return (
    <Container className='d-flex flex-column'>
        <Button className='m-3  p-4' variant='success' >Add type</Button>
        <Button className='m-3  p-4' variant='success' >Add Brand</Button>
        <Button className='m-3  p-4' variant='success' >Add device</Button>
        <TypeModal/>
    </Container>
  )
}

export default AdminPanel
